{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idcf8a95fd-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0","identifier":"/us/usc/t48/s1756"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1756"},"text":"§ 1756.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Lack of effect on covenant","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"No provision of this subchapter shall be construed to alter, amend, or abrogate any provision of the covenant referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t48/s1751"},"text":"section 1751 of this title","children":[],"tail":" except section 901 of the covenant."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idcf8a95fe-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/229/tVII/s716"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–229, title VII, § 716","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-08"},"text":"May 8, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/869"},"text":"122 Stat. 869","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idcf8a95ff-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idcf8a9600-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idcf8a9601-3a70-11f1-9e44-df1065572ea0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this subtitle”, meaning subtitle B (§§ 711–718) of title VII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/229"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–229","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-08"},"text":"May 8, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/868"},"text":"122 Stat. 868","children":[],"tail":", which enacted this subchapter and amended sections 4342, 6954 and 9432 of Title 10, Armed Forces. For complete classification of subtitle B to the Code, see Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The covenant, referred to in text, is the Covenant to Establish a Commonwealth of the Northern Mariana Islands in Political Union with the United States of America, which is contained in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/241/s1"},"text":"section 1 of Pub. L. 94–241","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t48/s1801"},"text":"section 1801 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
